# Frontend (Vite) environment.
# Copy to interface/.env only if you need to override defaults.
#
# In dev, `npm run dev` proxies /api and /media to http://localhost:4000
# (see vite.config.ts), so no configuration is required for local use.
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to the app.

# VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api
